13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 3, Chapter 291, O.S.L.
15 2024 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 538.3), is amended to read as
16 follows:
17 Section 538.3. A. A laser practitioner shall only perform
18 laser hair removal using lasers or pulsed light devices approved by
19 the United States Food and Drug Administration (FDA) for noninvasive
20 procedures.
21 B. A person shall not perform or attempt to perform laser hair
22 removal unless the person holds the appropriate health professional
23 license or certificate as defined in Section 2 538.2 of this act
24 title, unless the person is a laser practitioner performing laser
