11 of Nursing.
12 H. G. Nothing in this act shall prohibit any person in the
13 healing arts, in this state, under any other act, from engaging in
14 the practice for which he or she is duly licensed.
15 SECTION 2. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
16 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
